description:
Commercial Tables perfect for use in hotels, café's and restaurants. Matched with our commercial dining chairs. Quality manufacturing and durable designs make our range of dining tables hard wearing and suitable for all environments. Our tables are available in standard finishes or with a wide choice of table top finishes and table base frame colours including glass solid wood, aluminium and powder coated options. We offer:
  • Traditional Wooden Tables,
  • Laminate Tables,
  • Glass Tables,
  • Teak, EZ Care & Werzalit Tables.
